high_descs: Turn right towards the dresser on which microwave oven is placed
Open the oven and take a credit card from it and close the oven
Turn left and take few steps and again take a left turn to reach the desk
Put the credit card on the left top of the desk
Little bit move towards the right side and reach the dresser again
Open the oven and take one more credit card from it and close the oven
Turn left and take few steps and again take a left turn to reach the desk once again
Put the credit card next to the first card on the left top of the desk
anns.task_desc: Put the credit card on the desk

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dresser to your left
Pick up credit card from the dresser
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the desk
Place credit card on the corner of the desk
Turn around and head right and walk to the dresser to your left
Pick up credit card from the dresser
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the desk
Place credit card on the corner of the desk
anns.task_desc: Arranging credit card on the desk

high_descs: Turn around and go to the dresser
Take out one credit from the dresser
Turn your left and go to the desk
Place the credit card on the desk
Move back to the dresser again
Take out one more credit card from the dresser
Turn around and walk back to the desk again
Place the credit card on the desk
anns.task_desc: Move the credit cards from desk to dresser
